                                                 class="material-icons right">more_vert</i></span>
                                               <p>Click for some first aid tips</p>
                                             </div>
                                             <div class="card-reveal">
                                               <span class="card-title grey-text text-darken-4">Some First Tips<i class="material-icons right">close</i></span>
                                               <p>-if you get pepper in your eyes, wash you hand thoroughly,  soak a cotton ball in cold milk and place over the affected eye,
                                             you can also use for fingers for this
                                              <br>-for skin, rub alcohol on affected area, then soak the skin in milk or another dairy product 
                                               <br>-do not use water as this spreads the pepper even further 
                                                
                                                </p>
