                             <div class="card-content">
                               <span class="card-title activator grey-text text-darken-4">ELECTROCUTION<i
                                 class="material-icons right">more_vert</i></span>
                               <p>Click for some first aid tips</p>
                             </div>
                             <div class="card-reveal">
                               <span class="card-title grey-text text-darken-4">Some First Tips<i class="material-icons right">close</i></span>
                               <p>-Switch off current or cut the supply by removing the plug or breaking the cable. Do not attempt to do this with a scissors or knife
                               <br> - Remove the patient from the contact with great care using dry insulating materials like gloves, folded cloth or newspaper 
                                <br>- If patient is conscious, reassure the patient
                                <br>- Lay the person down on thier back with the head low and turned to one side
                               <br> - Loosen clothing around neck, chest and waist
                               <br> - wrap them in a blanket 
                               <br> - Give sips of water, or any liquid except alcohol
                                <br>- Seek immediate medical attention 
                                
                                
                                </p>
